These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, firefighter, electrician
The people use 3 different means of transport: tram, train, helicopter
1. the person driving the tram is not to the left of the person driving the helicopter##8
2. the electrician is somewhere to the right of the person driving the helicopter##5
3. the person driving the helicopter is between the firefighter and the electrician##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |     3      |
| Job         | firefighter | dancer   | electrician |
| Transport   | train | helicopter | tram        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, almond-milk, juice
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, snake, ferret
1. the person drinking fanta is somewhere between the person drinking juice and the owner of the guinea-pig##7
2. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
3. the owner of the snake is not to the right of the person drinking fanta##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |     3      |
| Beverage   | juice | fanta   | almond-milk   |
| Pet        | snake | ferret | guinea-pig |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-3::.
There 3 different types of food: garlic, grapefruit, pineapple
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, trike, bike
1. the person eating garlic is not to the left of the person driving the trike##8
2. the person eating pineapple is somewhere between the person eating garlic and the person driving the scooter##7
3. the person eating pineapple is not to the left of the person driving the bike##8
4. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |
| Food        | grapefruit | pineapple | garlic |
| Transport   | scooter       | bike     | trike         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  musician, freelancer, security-guard
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, disaster, mystery
1. the security-guard is not to the right of the freelancer##8
2. the security-guard is on the right of the musician##1
3. the person watching musical movies is somewhere between the person watching disaster movies and the musician##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Job           | musician | security-guard | freelancer |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery  | musical | disaster    |

