.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, action, fantasy
3 different pets are kept: frog, chinchilla, pony
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
3. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching scientific movies##5
4. the person watching action movies is not to the right of the person watching scientific movies##8
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
6. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the owner of the frog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | action | fantasy | scientific |
| Pet           | chinchilla    | pony      | frog  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-6::.
