2. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the right of the chef##5
3. the journalist is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
4. the architect is on the left of the chef##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |   2    |       3        |
| Job   | architect | chef | journalist |
| Pet   | pony        | fish   | rabbit     |

