The people have 3 different jobs:  musician, manager, electrician
1. the manager is between the electrician and the person drinking fanta##2
2. the person drinking juice is not to the left of the electrician##8
3. the person drinking fanta is not to the left of the electrician##8
4. the electrician is the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | milk | juice | fanta |
| Job        | electrician      | manager    | musician |

