2. the person eating cucumber is somewhere to the left of the person eating peas##5
3. the person watching documentary movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching mystery movies is not to the right of the person eating asparagus##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |
| Food          | cucumber | asparagus  | peas |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary     | mystery | fantasy   |

