.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, water, iced-tea
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, parkour, lacrosse
1. the person drinking iced-tea is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is not to the left of the person drinking water##8
3. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5
4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
5. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |       2       |    3     |
| Beverage   | water | iced-tea        | fanta    |
| Sport      | parkour  | lacrosse | surfing |

