.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-17::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: jazz, gospel, techno
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, skateboarding, parkour
1. the fan of techno is not to the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##8
2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the fan of techno##1
3. the fan of techno is between the fan of gospel and the fan of jazz##2
4. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
5. the fan of gospel is not to the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Music-Genre   | jazz       | techno      | gospel |
| Sport         | skiing | skateboarding | parkour     |

