3. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the person eating radish##5
4. the person eating pineapple is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3
5. the person eating radish is on the left of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |     2     |     3      |
| Food   | banana | radish | pineapple    |
| Pet    | turtle   | mouse      | rat |

