3. the person watching crime movies is somewhere between the person watching fantasy movies and the person watching drama movies##7
4. the person watching drama movies is not to the left of the egyptian##8
5. the egyptian is not to the left of the person watching crime movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy   | crime    | drama  |
| Nationality   | mexican | polish | egyptian |

