.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, woodworking, rock-climbing
There are 3 different nationalities: indian, canadian, dutch
1. the canadian is somewhere between the dutch and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##7
2. the indian is not to the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##8
3. the indian is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |      3      |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | woodworking | rock-climbing |
| Nationality   | dutch  | canadian    | indian    |

 